# opencode import

> Import session data from a JSON file or URL.
> More information: <https://opencode.ai/docs/cli#import>.

- Import from a JSON file:

`opencode import {{path/to/session}}.json`

- Import from a share URL:

`opencode import {{URL}}`

- Display help:

`opencode import {{[-h|--help]}}`
